WEBVTT

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:32.016
About this time, I looked
all around the circle I was in,

00:01:32.040 --> 00:01:35.400
and all the kids had stopped playing
and they were all looking at me.

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:37.696
And I'm thinking --

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:41.496
in today's language,
it would be "OMG" or "WTF."

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:44.160
(Laughter)

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:47.080
What just happened?

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:51.856
So all the confidence
that I went in with that morning

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:55.216
was withering away as the morning went on

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.920
and the questions kept coming.

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.176
And at the end of the morning,
before I went home,